txt.en: There is much to be done in the maggot-hole caverns of Skoironk.
Enter the maggot-hole caverns of Skoironk
The Orcs down here are organized and camps litter the cavern floors. You believe that destroying some of these camps would give you and the Rangers an advantage in the Slag-hills.
The maggot-hole caverns of Skoironk are located in the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should destroy Orkish tents in Skoironk.
The maggot-hole caverns of Skoironk are located in the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should destroy Orkish tents in Skoironk.
You have destroyed many tents within the maggot-hole caverns of Skoironk. This should lessen the effectiveness of the Orcs camped down here.
